@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/aboutstyle.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-page">
        <div class="background">
            <div class="overlay"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <section class="values-origin">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <div class="text-container">
                        <h1>Values and Origin of Our Foundation:</h1>
                        <p>
                            Welcome to the Bumblebee Foundation, established in 2020 as a Non-Profit Company with a clear mission: to serve as a conduit for both local and offshore sponsors seeking to make a meaningful impact within South Africa. Our primary focus lies in fostering partnerships with offshore sponsors, leveraging their resources to support the initiatives of other non profit organisations.

                            At the heart of our foundation is the belief in the power of collaboration and collective action. We understand that real change happens when individuals and organisations come together to address pressing social and environmental challenges. By harnessing the generosity of offshore sponsors and facilitating their support for local initiatives, we strive to create a ripple effect of positive change that extends far beyond geographical boundaries.

                            Our approach is centred around transparency, accountability, and sustainability. We are committed to ensuring that every rand contributed to the Bumblebee Foundation is used efficiently and effectively to support the causes that matter most to us. Through strategic partnerships, we aim to maximise the impact of every donation, no matter how large or small.

                            We strive to work towards a brighter, more equitable future for all less fortunate and in despondence poverty. Together, we can create lasting change and leave a legacy of compassion and generosity for generations to come.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-image">
                        <img src="/images/bee.png" alt="bee on flower" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="vision">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <div class="text-container">
                        <h2>Vision Statement:</h2>
                        <p>
                            At Bumblebee Foundation, we envision a place where every individual and community has the opportunity to thrive.
                            We strive for a future where social and environmental challenges are met with empathy, innovation, and collaboration.
                            Our vision is one of interconnectedness, where offshore sponsors and local initiatives unite to create sustainable solutions that leave a lasting impact.
                            Through our dedication to transparency, accountability, and inclusivity, we aspire to be a beacon of hope and catalyst for positive change worldwide.
                            Together, we can build a future where everyone has the resources and support they need to reach their full potential.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-image">
                        <img src="/images/groupphoto.jpg" alt="Group Photo">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mission">
                <div class="content-container">
                    <div class="text-container">
                        <h2>Mission Statement:</h2>
                        <p>
                            The Bumblebee Foundation is dedicated to fostering partnerships and mobilising resources to support the initiatives of
                            non-profit organisations within South Africa. Our mission is to connect offshore sponsors with local projects,
                            amplifying their impact and empowering communities to address pressing social and environmental challenges.
                            Committed to transparency, accountability, and sustainability, we strive to maximize the effectiveness of every donation
                            and ensure that resources are directed towards meaningful, long-term solutions. Through collaboration and collective action,
                            we aim to create a more equitable and resilient space for present and future generations.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="section-image">
                        <img src="/images/money.jpg" alt="Jar of Money">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="directors">
                <h3>Bumble Bee Foundation Directors</h3>
            </section>

            <footer class="directors-footer">
                <div class="directors-container">
                    <div class="director">
                        <img src="/images/Bee Pfp.png" alt="Asha Reuben Murray">
                        <p>Asha Reuben Murray</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="director">
                        <img src="/images/Bee Pfp.png" alt="Leelawatlie Meth">
                        <p>Leelawatlie Meth</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="director">
                        <img src="/images/Bee Pfp.png" alt="Anisha Owthar">
                        <p>Anisha Owthar</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </footer>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
